# Asset placeholder directory — kept in git via this .gitkeep file.
#
# Drop the following Kodi 21 (Omega) addon artwork into this directory
# (resources/) before packaging the addon:
#
#   icon.png    — 256x256 px, PNG with transparency, addon launcher icon.
#                 Referenced from addon.xml as:
#                   <assets><icon>resources/icon.png</icon></assets>
#
#   fanart.jpg  — 1280x720 px, JPEG, full-bleed background art shown in
#                 the addon browser and on plugin root.
#                 Referenced from addon.xml as:
#                   <assets><fanart>resources/fanart.jpg</fanart></assets>
#
# Keep both files under ~500 KB combined so the addon stays lightweight
# on the Raspberry Pi 3B+ target (~380 MB total install budget).
